Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コケティッシュ｡➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:55.29,Default,N,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soft enough for your skin. Soft enough for my skin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:56.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の肌にも コケティッシュ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:56.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,コレコレケｯコー コケティｯシｭ｡➡\N
