Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[ﾗｼﾞｵ](ＤＪ)\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいかい？カール君➡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.35,Default,DJ,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen up, Carl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:39.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,答えはね…君次第だよ｡\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:39.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだそりゃ！\N
